					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-767497#post-1945638</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-767497/scp-1874#post-1945638</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2014 02:10:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zolgamax</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1707551</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Seems good enough to me. It's nice and simple. Not every article has to be some huge, ominous threat to reality. The terrorist attack on the petting zoo was a nice touch.</p> <p>A bit of explanation as to how the sheep actually explodes, even if very brief, would help a lot. Mentioning some organs that overheat/hyperinflate when the sheep gets stressed, or something along those, might help. Sheep normally produce a lot of methane, which ties in nicely with the explosions.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
