					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-767497#post-1945620</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-767497/scp-1874#post-1945620</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2014 01:56:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Eskobar</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1173523</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>The required protective gear is to be worn at all times in the vicinity of SCP-1874. I don't know why I should even have to reiterate this fact, but we're still cleaning up what's left of D-1357 after he disobeyed this protocol. - Dr. Waverton</p> </blockquote> <p>As far as end-article addenda go, this is not quite lolfoundation, but it doesn't paint the Foundation in the best light. The required protective gear is&#8230;<em>required protective gear</em>. I don't know why you had to reiterate this fact either. And the fact that you inserted yourself into your first article&#8230;it's not forbidden or anything, but it can bug some people.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
